title: Vulcan Death Grip by Old Gray
lyrics:
"- What did you do?"
"- I was unprepared for his attack. I instinctively used the Vulcan death grip."

You said that everything would be okay
And that we could settle down, in a house by the river
Well, look at us now
(Whoo!)
I don’t know where I am, I don’t know where I will go

Maybe someday you will love me but I don’t think that I can wait
Maybe someday you will love me but I don’t think that I can wait Maybe someday you will love me but I don’t think that I can wait Maybe someday you will love me but I don’t think that I can wait Maybe someday you will love me but I don’t think that I can wait
